## 2. Operating Environment

### 2.1 Runtime
- **Browser:** Chrome 120+ / Safari 17+ / Firefox 121+
- **Dev Server:** Vite (`localhost:5173`)
- **Backend:** LiE FastAPI (`localhost:8000`)
- **Node.js:** 20 LTS+

### 2.2 Tech Stack

| Layer | Choice | Reason |
|-------|--------|--------|
| Framework | React 18 + Vite | Fast HMR, lightweight bundle |
| UI Components | shadcn/ui | High quality, copy-owned, Next.js-migratable |
| Styling | Tailwind CSS v3 | Utility-first, consistent with shadcn |
| HTTP Client | axios or fetch | Lightweight, no extra dependency required |
| State | React Context + useState | Sufficient for Standard scope |
| Auth State | localStorage (JWT) | Simple, matches backend Bearer token model |

### 2.3 Deployment Model
Served locally only. No CDN, no cloud hosting. Vite dev server or `vite build` + static file serving on localhost.

