## 3. User Roles

| Role | Login Required | Query | Upload |
|------|---------------|-------|--------|
| Researcher | ✅ | ✅ | ❌ |
| Lab PI | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ |
| Admin | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ |

Role is determined by JWT payload returned from `POST /auth/token`. UI elements that exceed the user's role shall be hidden or disabled.

