## 8. API Integration

| UI Action | Backend Endpoint | Method |
|-----------|-----------------|--------|
| Login | `/auth/token` | POST |
| Submit query | `/query` | POST |
| Upload document | `/ingest` | POST |
| Health check | `/health` | GET |

All authenticated requests shall include `Authorization: Bearer <token>` header, injected automatically via an axios interceptor in `lib/api.ts`.

