## 11. Risks

| Risk | Mitigation |
|------|------------|
| CORS error on localhost | Configure FastAPI `CORSMiddleware` for `localhost:5173` |
| JWT expiry mid-session | Detect 401 response, auto-redirect to login |
| LaTeX rendering bundle size | Use KaTeX (lighter than MathJax) |
| shadcn/ui version drift | Pin component versions, copy-owned pattern |